## Default domain translations template.
##
## String-based msgids — use the English text directly as the key.
## Platform-specific overrides go in {platform}.po files (optional).
## Non-English translations go in locale-specific default.po files.
##
## To add translations:
## 1. Add msgid here with empty msgstr (the English string is the key)
## 2. Run `mix gettext.merge priv/gettext`
## 3. Add platform overrides in platform .po files if needed

## Example keys - replace with your actual strings

